Liesl Bebb-McKay is head of innovation and disruption at Rand Merchant Bank (RMB) Global Markets. In this video interview she answers the following questions: 1. How did Project Athena come together?
2. What influenced the name of the project?
3. What has the project achieved so far?
4. Why is banking so male dominated? Are we seeing change?
5. Why are women often reluctant to join an investment bank, or, if they do, seemingly leave very soon after? This video was produced by Moneyweb with journalist Nastassia Arendse, and sponsored by RMB.